This is a list of tasks of the main faults that can be seen at each given time
and that have to be solved for the SORB.

Release 2
	Write some code to emulate the page swapping IPC mechanism while the
code is not ported to a real Alliance System.
	Use this IPC code to implement the threaded servers.

Release 1
	Write some code to emulate the page swapping IPC mechanism while the
code is not ported to a real Alliance System.
	Use this IPC code to implement the threaded servers.
	Modify the source tree and the code according the the Coding Guidelines